Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露疗法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爷  您在哪
